me will help in improving the overall quality of ITIs across the country.ITIs were previously under Labour Ministry which now have been transferred to Skill Ministry since 2015. PMRF scheme will address our national priorities at one hand and shortage of quality faculty on the other hand.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}